*Vašim* rukama stvaram svoju sudbinu. (With your hands I create my own destiny.)

Kako biste *vašim* uspesima udovoljili potrebama? (How would you meet the needs with your successes?)

*Vašim* delima ćeš biti poznat. (You will be known by your deeds.)

*Vašim* detinjstvom ću se uvek radovati. (I will always rejoice in your childhood.)

*Vašim* uspehom ćemo se diviti. (We will be amazed by your success.)